            <div class="file-content" onclick="selectAll(this)"># ğŸ´â€â˜ ï¸ One Piece Discord Voice Bot

A Discord bot that creates dynamic voice channels with authentic One Piece locations and ships! Set sail with your crew and explore the Grand Line together!

## â­ Features

- ğŸš¢ **Dynamic Voice Channels** - Automatically creates channels when needed
- ğŸï¸ **Lore-Accurate Names** - 30+ authentic One Piece locations and ships
- ğŸ‘‘ **Captain Permissions** - Channel creators get admin rights
- ğŸŒŠ **Auto-Cleanup** - Empty crews disband automatically
- ğŸ´â€â˜ ï¸ **Pirate Theme** - Full One Piece immersion with themed messages

## ğŸš€ Quick Start

1. **Install dependencies**
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

2. **Configure your bot**
   ```bash
   cp .env.example .env
   # Edit .env with your Discord bot token
   ```

3. **Start the bot**
   ```bash
   npm start
   ```

## ğŸ“– Bot Setup

1. Create a Discord Application at [Discord Developer Portal](https://discord.com/developers/applications)
2. Create a Bot and copy the token
3. Add the token to your `.env` file
4. Invite the bot with these permissions:
   - Manage Channels
   - Connect
   - Move Members
   - View Channels

## ğŸ´â€â˜ ï¸ How It Works

1. Join "ğŸ´â€â˜ ï¸ Set Sail Together" channel
2. Bot creates a new pirate crew with a One Piece themed name
3. You become the captain with admin permissions
4. Empty crews automatically disband after 5 seconds

